This is the source code for the article Integrating Open Authentication Using
Opauth by Rakhitha Nimesh available at
http://sitepoint.com/integrating-open-authentication-using-opauth

* Copy the contents of config.php file to CodeIgniter config file located at
  applications/config.
* Copy Opauth_lib directory and Opauth_lib.php file to applications/libraries
  directory.
* Copy the auth.php file to applications/controllers directory.
* Access the login links using http://example.com/auth/login
